export const homeObjOne = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,

    alt: 'Vault'
  };
  
  export const homeObjThree = {
    lightBg: true,

    lightTextDesc: false,

    alt: 'Vault'
  };
  
  export const homeObjFour = {
